00:00:24.766 --> 00:00:26.701 position:19% line:89% align:start
♪ The seasons change

00:00:26.736 --> 00:00:28.337 position:16% line:89% align:start
♪ As I change with them

00:00:28.371 --> 00:00:31.741 position:13% line:89% align:start
♪ And the call of spring

00:00:31.774 --> 00:00:34.277 position:21% line:89% align:start
♪ Gives me strength

00:00:34.311 --> 00:00:37.947 position:19% line:89% align:start
♪ And courage to know

00:00:37.980 --> 00:00:42.052 position:13% line:5% align:start
♪ I will make it through

00:00:42.085 --> 00:00:46.056 position:7% line:5% align:start
♪ Whatever life throws at me

